    "Name": "Black Knight",
    "Details": "The Black Knight BL-15-KNT is an upgrade of the BL6-KNT. The antiquated single heat sinks were removed, along with the standard armor and all but three medium lasers. The BL-15-KNT instead  mounts thirteen double heat sinks, a Gauss rifle, two ER large lasers, and three medium lasers. As a weight-saving measure, the BL-15 also uses ferro-fibrous armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Command Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>",
